name: WKMenuItemIcon
desc: Template images that you can use for menus.

items.name: case accept
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to accept an event or item.

items.name: case add
items.desc: The icon indicating an action for adding an item.

items.name: case block
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to block or prevent something from happening.

items.name: case decline
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to decline or cancel an event.

items.name: case info
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to retrieve more information.

items.name: case maybe
items.desc: The icon indicating an answer of maybe for an action.

items.name: case more
items.desc: The icon indicating that more actions or options are available.

items.name: case mute
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to mute the sound.

items.name: case pause
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to pause playback.

items.name: case play
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to play some content.

items.name: case `repeat`
items.desc: The icon indicating that played content should repeat in a loop.

items.name: case resume
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to resume playing some content.

items.name: case share
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to share content.

items.name: case shuffle
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to shuffle content.

items.name: case trash
items.desc: The icon indicating an action to delete some content.
